dct_title_s: A topographical map of a part of northern New Jersey [sheet 2, east part]
dct_description_sm: Covers Newark region and adjacent part of New York City. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Includes notes. Historic Maps copy 2 imperfect: upper portion of sheet 2 torn; sheet 1 wanting.
dct_publisher_sm: [Trenton?] : Geological Survey of New Jersey, 1882 (Julius Bien, lith.)
